{"image_id": "WU_2010_page_66", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "Critical Accounting Policies and Estimates", "bbox": [143.8, 116.6, 527.9, 137.5]}, {"text": "Management’s discussion and analysis of results of operations and financial condition is based on our financial", "bbox": [168.8, 154.1, 1093.7, 175.0]}, {"text": "statements that have been prepared in accordance with accounting principles generally accepted in the United", "bbox": [143.8, 179.2, 1094.1, 200.0]}, {"text": "States. The preparation of these financial statements requires that management make estimates and assumptions", "bbox": [143.8, 204.1, 1094.2, 224.9]}, {"text": "that affect the amounts reported for revenues, expenses, assets, liabilities and other related disclosures. Actual", "bbox": [143.8, 229.1, 1093.9, 250.0]}, {"text": "results may or may not differ from these estimates. Our significant accounting policies are discussed in Note 2,", "bbox": [143.8, 254.2, 1094.2, 275.0]}, {"text": "Summary of Significant Accounting Policies, of the notes to consolidated financial statements, included in Item 8,", "bbox": [143.8, 279.1, 1094.2, 300.0]}, {"text": "Financial Statements and Supplementary Data.", "bbox": [143.8, 304.2, 545.1, 325.0]}, {"text": "Our critical accounting policies and estimates, described below, are very important to the portrayal of our", "bbox": [168.8, 341.6, 1094.1, 362.5]}, {"text": "financial position and our results of operations and applying them requires our management to make difficult,", "bbox": [143.8, 366.7, 1094.0, 387.5]}, {"text": "subjective and complex judgments. We believe that the understanding of these key accounting policies and", "bbox": [143.8, 391.7, 1094.0, 412.6]}, {"text": "estimates is essential in achieving more insight into our operating results and financial condition.", "bbox": [143.8, 416.6, 974.4, 437.5]}, {"text": "Description", "bbox": [260.3, 465.9, 340.8, 482.5]}, {"text": "Judgments and Uncertainties", "bbox": [511.2, 465.9, 716.6, 482.5]}, {"text": "Effect if Actual Results Differ from", "bbox": [812.6, 449.1, 1062.5, 465.8]}, {"text": "Assumptions", "bbox": [892.9, 465.9, 982.5, 482.5]}, {"text": "Income Taxes", "bbox": [154.3, 498.0, 275.2, 518.9]}, {"text": "Reinvestment of foreign earnings", "bbox": [154.3, 520.9, 428.2, 541.7]}, {"text": "Income taxes, as reported in our", "bbox": [154.3, 555.4, 424.0, 576.2]}, {"text": "consolidated financial statements,", "bbox": [154.3, 578.3, 435.3, 599.1]}, {"text": "represent the net amount of", "bbox": [154.3, 601.2, 384.3, 622.0]}, {"text": "income taxes we expect to pay to", "bbox": [154.3, 624.1, 433.4, 645.0]}, {"text": "various taxing jurisdictions in", "bbox": [154.3, 647.0, 401.8, 667.9]}, {"text": "connection with our operations.", "bbox": [154.3, 670.0, 417.7, 690.8]}, {"text": "We provide for income taxes", "bbox": [154.3, 692.9, 395.1, 713.7]}, {"text": "based on amounts that we believe", "bbox": [154.3, 715.8, 436.4, 736.6]}, {"text": "we will ultimately owe after", "bbox": [154.3, 738.7, 388.2, 759.6]}, {"text": "applying the required analyses and", "bbox": [154.3, 761.6, 443.5, 782.5]}, {"text": "judgments.", "bbox": [154.3, 784.6, 244.7, 805.4]}, {"text": "With respect to earnings in certain", "bbox": [467.5, 555.4, 756.5, 576.2]}, {"text": "foreign jurisdictions, we have", "bbox": [467.5, 578.3, 713.4, 599.1]}, {"text": "provided for income taxes on such", "bbox": [467.5, 601.2, 756.4, 622.0]}, {"text": "earnings at a more favorable", "bbox": [467.5, 624.1, 706.0, 645.0]}, {"text": "income tax rate than the combined", "bbox": [467.5, 647.0, 758.2, 667.9]}, {"text": "United States federal and state", "bbox": [467.5, 670.0, 722.5, 690.8]}, {"text": "income tax rates because we", "bbox": [467.5, 692.9, 705.9, 713.7]}, {"text": "expect to reinvest these earnings", "bbox": [467.5, 715.8, 738.8, 736.6]}, {"text": "outside of the United States", "bbox": [467.5, 738.7, 699.7, 759.6]}, {"text": "indefinitely.", "bbox": [467.5, 761.6